hful to her with the dive instructor, that is why she does not want any man or anything serious in her life. She has a hard time expressing her true feelings. Everyone sees her as the \"bad\" sister, but deep down she is a very good person. She is afraid to be sensitive and betrayed, so she has a hard time showing her feelings towards Mariano. At the end of the story she lives in concubinage with Mariano and their  twin daughters Mariana Luc\u00eda and Luc\u00eda Mariana. \n* Natalie P\u00e9rez as Carla Estrella. Younger sister of Luc\u00eda and half sister of Virginia, Florencia and Miranda. She is 28 years old. She and Florencia were born on the same day of the same year. She is fun and a good person. The error of having planted in the church the love of her life torments her. Looking for more than friendship with some hotel employees, but it is not successful. She was only in love with Sebasti\u00e1n, who married her childhood friend after she left him planted on the altar. She falls in love with Lucho and they start dating. At the end of the novel she goes to work at an important hotel in New York.\n* [[Violeta Urtizberea]] as Florencia Estrella. Younger sister of Virginia, half sister of Luc\u00eda, Carla and Miranda. She is 28 years old. She and Carla were born on the same day of the same year. What characterizes her is her [[Tourette's syndrome]], which makes her say bad words when she gets nervous and at the least appropriate moments. She always felt the \"weird\" of the family, since with his syndrome she has trouble getting work and friends. For her, as a girl she suffered bullying. She is the most fun and dreamy of the sisters. She falls in love with Jazm\u00edn and marries her. At the end of the story she is the driver of a school transport and together with Jazm\u00edn they adopt Violeta and Melisa.\n* Justina Bustos<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.justinabustos.com/|title=Justina Bustos {{!}} Actress {{!}} Home|website=www.justinabustos.com|language=en|access-date=2017-12-30}}</ref> as Miranda Estrella. She is the younger sister of 24 years old. Product of a relationship that Mario Estrella had with his secretary, Coky. At the beginning of the novel her work was like [[Escort girl | escort]], and is known as \"M\u00eda\" for her clients. She hide great secrets that will gradually be revealed. She fell in love with Manuel, but after his departure to Chile she becames Federico's girlfriend. After Manuel's return she temporarily returns with him, ready to escape together. At that moment he is killed in cold blood and dies in her arms. Miranda falls back in love with Federico and begins a relationship with him. At the end of the story she fulfills her dream of succeeding as a singer.\n\n=== Co-Starting ===\n* [[Esteban Lamothe]] as Javier \"Javo\" Vald\u00e9s. He is the chef of the hotel, he accepted this position for being a friend of Carla and is Jazm\u00edn's best friend. He was married to Amanda, with whom he has a son, Santiago. He is rebellious and adventurous. He falls in love with Virginia from the first day he sees her at his father's wake. He had a brief affair with Lolita. At the end of the story he marries Virginia, they have a daughter named Elena Vald\u00e9s Estrella and he set up a caterin company with Jazm\u00edn and Federico.\n* [[Gonzalo Valenzuela]] as Manuel Eizaguirre. He is a Chilean lawyer who arrives in Buenos Aires escaping from economic problems he had in his country because of gambling. Meet Miranda as an escort and fall in love with her. He ends up working as a hotel lawyer and discovers great irregularities and secrets of Ignacio. He goes to Chile to settle pending accounts leaving Miranda shattered. Later he leaves the jail after the reduction of his sentence in exchange for testifying against a heavy people, the same ones who later put an end to his life from a shot in the chest when he was about to escape with Miranda.\n* Rafael Ferro as Ignacio Basile C\u00f3rdoba. He is not married to Virginia but claims to be her husband. He is a lawyer and has his own studio. He is a liar and manipulator. He is always trying to dominate Virginia's life. It was he who initiated Miranda in the exercise of prostitution.\n* [[Luciano Castro]] as Mariano Montenegro. He arrives at the hotel asking for work as a sender. He falls in love with Luc\u00eda, with whom he forms the most stable couple in the novel. It is fun and self-centered personality. At the end of the story he lives in concubinage with Luc\u00eda and their twin daughters Mariana Luc\u00eda and Luc\u00eda Mariana.\n* [[Nicol\u00e1s Riera]] as Leonardo \"Leo\" Loma. He is the hotel receptionist. He falls in love with Miranda but after Federico began a relationship with her he decides to forget her. Then he falls in love with Trini and begins a relationship with her.\n* [[Nicol\u00e1s Francella]] as Federico Alc\u00e1ntara. It is the bartender of the hotel. At first he falls in love with Lucia, but after the appearance of Mariano moves away from her. He becomes Carla's friend. He falls in love with Miranda with whom he begins a relationship. At the end of the story he puts a cater company next to Jazm\u00edn and Javo.\n* [[Nazareno Casero]] as Daniel \"Dani\" Caccavella. He meet Flor in a car accident and fall in love with her from day one. His family owns a refrigerator, he is fun and very romantic with Florencia. After she left him planted on the altar and he accepted his ex's love with Jazm\u00edn, he spends his time trying to seduce how many women he crosses his path.\n* Julieta Nair Calvo as Jazm\u00edn del R\u00edo. She is Javo's kitchen assistant and his best friend. She fell in love with Florencia from day one, but she can't be with her. After Flor left Dani planted at the altar, Florencia begins to doubt her sexuality and feelings towards Jazm\u00edn. After Flor accepted her love for her, they start a relationship and get married. At the end of the story, together with Flor, they adopt Violeta and Melisa and set up a catering company with Javo and Federico.\n\n=== Recurring ===\n* [[Silvia Kutika]] as Teresa de Estrella. Mario's first wife and mother of Virginia and Florencia.\n* Patricia Etchegoyen as Mar\u00eda Elisa Casal. Second wife of Mario Estrella and mother of Luc\u00eda and Carla.\n* Patricia Viggiano as Constanza \"Coky\" Calmet. Being Mario's secretary, she fell in love with him. She is Miranda's mother.\n* [[Ezequiel Rodr\u00edguez (actor)|Ezequiel Rodr\u00edguez]] as Sebasti\u00e1n Le Brun. Psychologist. He is Carla's ex. He is married to Nadia, but has the desire to return with Carla Estrella.\n* [[In\u00e9s Palombo]] as Nadia Guti\u00e9rrez. Carla's high school classmate and Sebasti\u00e1n's wife.\n* Maia Francia as Amanda. Javo's wife. It is part of Ignacio's plan to separate Javo from Virginia.\n* Andr\u00e9s Gil as Dami\u00e1n. Miranda University classmate.\n* Jazm\u00edn Falak as Delfina L\u00f3pez Mayo. Former schoolmate of Carla and daughter of Fern\u00e1n.\n* Miriam Odorico as Mu\u00f1eca. Hotel maid suffers from short-term amnesia. She is in love with Ignacio.\n* [[Vanesa Gonz\u00e1lez]] as Milagros \"Lolita\" Guzm\u00e1n. She is attracted to Javo and had a brief affair with him. Her real name is Milagros and 10 years before the events of history she escaped from the family home in San Mart\u00edn de los Andes due to the constant abuse of his grandmother. Subsequently, she became a hotel patchwork and reunited with his brother, with whom he re-established his bond thanks to Javo. At the end of the story, after not being able to force the relationship with Javo anymore since she continues without forgetting Virginia, she decides to cut with him and return to San Mart\u00edn de los Andes.\n* Pedro Alfonso as Luis \u00c1ngel \"Lucho\" Solar. He is Mariano's cousin and becomes the hotel manager. He falls in love with Carla and they start a relationship. He had a brief affair with Camila. At the end of the story he left the hotel management after the closure of the hotel and became commissioner on board to be closer to Carla who went to work in New York.\n* [[Mart\u00edn Seefeld]] como Fern\u00e1n Kowacksinsky. Luc\u00eda\u2019s Gynecologist and father of Delfina. He falls in love with Carla and they start a relationship.\n* [[Osvaldo Laport]] as Mario Estrella. He is the father of the girls. He lied to all his daughters and his ex-wives that he was dead.\n* Macarena Paz es Mar\u00eda Trinidad \"Trini\". New hotel employee. She falls in love with Leo and begins a relationship with him.\n\n=== Special participations ===\n* [[Silvina Luna]] as Julia R\u00edos. Mariano's ex girlfriend. She is Anita's mother and is imprisoned. She got a job at the hotel, but left after realizing his ex's relationship with Luc\u00eda.\n* [[Silvina Bosco]] as Diana. Luc\u00eda's psychologist. \n* [[Gustavo Conti]] as Felipe. Lucho's friend.\n* [[Martina Stoessel]] as Herself\n* [[Sebasti\u00e1n Yatra]] as Sebasti\u00e1n Ordo\u00f1ez. He is a young man with a great physical resemblance to singer Sebasti\u00e1n Yatra who is dedicated to imitate him.\n* [[Benjam\u00edn Alfonso]] as Juan Segundo \u201cJuanse\u201d Faulkner. Son of the heart of Eduardo Estrella.\n* [[Luciano Pereyra]] as Himself\n* Florencia Otero as Elena. Jazm\u00edn's ex girlfriend. She is an assistant scientist of Dr. Escolano, works in the Marti group.\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://www.eltrecetv.com.ar/las-estrellas Official site]\n* [https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCYDli2cqXJahEj0hQMmmrGQ Youtube channel]\n* {{IMDb title|6916086|Las Estrellas}}\n\n{{Pol-ka}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Estrellas (telenovela)}}\n[[Category:2017 telenovelas]]\n[[Category:2017 Argentine television series debuts]]\n[[Category:2018 Argentine television series endings]]\n[[Category:Pol-ka telenovelas]]\n[[Category:Spanish-language telenovelas]]\n[[Category:Argentine LGBT-related television shows]]\n[[Category:Lesbian-related television programs]]\n[